text: Mohawk is a 1956 American historical drama movie directed by Kurt Neumann and starring Scott Brady, Rita Gam, Neville Brand, Lori Nelson, Allison Hayes, John Hoyt, John Hudson. It was distributed by the 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1956 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies directed by Kurt Neumann
